thread.title: Rob Gough
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Rob Gough

author: Rob Gough
title: Rob Gough
text: Roland Paterson and his team at Nelson Alexander Fitzroy have delivered a hassle-free, professional and effective marketing campaign and auction for our house in North Fitzroy. Their advice was balanced with thoughtful explanations provided every step of the way. Our expectations were exceeded and as such we have no hesitation in recommending Roland and the team!
